"manieroj."

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/color-calibrate-screen.page:47
msgid "Make sure your calibration device is connected to your computer."
msgstr "Certigu ke via kalibradaparato estas konektita al via komputilo."

#. (itstool) path: item/p
