msgid "Variable refresh rate (VRR)"
msgstr "Variabla refreŝigfrekvenco (VRR)"

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/look-resolution.page:134
msgid ""
"For smoother visuals and to optimize power consumption you can synchronize "
